The Apache Commons Net library believes that the `220` response from the server does not conform to RFC 959 (probably rightfully).

If you want to allow the library to talk to the server, call [`FTP.setStrictReplyParsing`](https://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-net/apidocs/org/apache/commons/net/ftp/FTP.html#setStrictReplyParsing(boolean)):

    ftpClient.setStrictReplyParsing(false);

